&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&&



This is a tiny little program which causes the RamDisk icon to
act like other disk icons that you have on your Workbench:
ie. Snapshot the Ram icon in place, reset your computer and the
thing will be in the same place you left it. What an innovation!


@{jleft}

       @{" Requirements " Link reqs}    What you need to run RamSnap
       @{" Notes        " Link notes}    Notes on RamSnap
       @{" The Author   " Link Author}    Who's Responsible

       @{" Registration " Link joke}    RamSnap is FREEWARE!
        
        
        
        
